metadata.name: Goddess of Volcano
metadata.description:
My first NFT. 

She was burning inside but her blue skin would cool the fire... this war between her blue surface and red essence made her a Goddess...


" Satan: "Me miserable! Which way shall I fly
Infinite wrath and infinite despair?
Which way I fly is hell; myself am hell... "
John Milton, Paradise Lost


Oil paint on canvas (50x70)
Painted on 2019-06-28

Res: 2000 × 2828
